{"tid":1886909,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國外交部指華爾街日報文章惡意抹黑中國　吊銷3名記者駐京證","createTime":"2020-02-19T08:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T13:37:22.000Z","uid":212626,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4cbca42f324c526272463ced47f92a224b87e9ce","tid":1886909,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:20:36.000Z","msg":"中國外交部表示，美國《華爾街日報》發表辱華文章後拒絕道歉及問責，決定即日起吊銷該報3名駐京記者的記者證。<br />\n<br />\n發言人耿爽在外交部網上記者會表示，該報本月3日刊發美國巴德學院教授米德撰寫的評論文章，詆譭中國政府和中國人民抗擊疫情的努力，報社編輯還加上<span style=\"color: red;\">《中國是真正的東亞病夫》</span>這種帶有種族歧視色彩的聳人聽聞標題，引起中國人民極大憤慨和國際社會廣泛譴責。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽表示，已經多次向該報提出嚴正交涉，但報社至今仍在推諉、搪塞，既未公開正式道歉，也未查處相關責任人。他說，中國人民不歡迎發表種族歧視言論、惡意抹黑攻擊中國的媒體，因此決定吊銷3名駐京記者的記者證，中方將繼續按照國際慣例，依法為各國記者在華採訪提供支持及便利。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509478-20200219.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509478-20200219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDiRJil42CLA7NmQUB0MJ4tY%3D&h=7cc4aa60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509478-20200219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=24f3bb45\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509478-20200219.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebbe4c25705ceb04615c4f64d1104b4d4b2ccc41","tid":1886909,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">求入去幫推及rt + like + reply</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【19/2 twitter *極度*要人】美國議員全方位怒插中共<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1886899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1886899</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2f06cc59658941d189c13f3896c30cf9b8583180","tid":1886909,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0